### 环比：最近两个等长周期对比（prevStart/prevEnd 传 null，自动计算上期）
POST http://localhost:8087/test/tool/month-over-month
Content-Type: application/json

{
"currentStart": "2026-04-01",
"currentEnd": "2026-04-30",
"prevStart": null,
"prevEnd": null,
"regionName": null
}

### 同比：今年 vs 去年同期（全公司）
POST http://localhost:8087/test/tool/year-over-year
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2026-03-01",
  "endDate": "2026-04-30",
  "regionName": null
}

